Description: Unified, device-aware pipelines to load, calibrate, epoch, and compute common summary metrics (MIMS, AI, ENMO, MAD, ROCAM) from ActiGraph, Axivity, and GENEActiv devices. Includes optional non-wear detection and a universal driver.
